## Boundary Statement

This registry is dependency visibility only. It does not authorize implementation, integration, production publication, production credentials, treasury movement, wallet signing, trading, DEX execution, marketplace settlement, mining payouts, lottery payouts, ACS provisioning, on-chain writes, governance execution, billing execution or production readiness.

